            "extra_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Have you ever gone to the \"Scar of the Land\", Sophie?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "No. I've heard things about it, but I've never gone there yet."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "What kind of place is it?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x1c,
            "expr_id": 0xb,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "To put it in one word, it's a wasteland."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "A wasteland?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x1d,
            "expr_id": 0xb,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "There's no water, and sheer cliffs. That might be why there are materials that you can't find in normal places."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Huh, so it's a place like that?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x1e,
            "expr_id": 0xb,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "I remembered it because it might be useful for your alchemy."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "I see. Thank you, Elise. I'll try going there sometime."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x43,
            "expr_id": 0xb,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "I hear there are strong monsters there, so you should be careful."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Oh. Okay."
